    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those responsible for erecting structures or buildings of any kind. Builders include the company that is responsible for the construction, as well as groups or individual professional people who receive instructions from an architect or patron, and employ other workers to carry out manual labor.</Note_Text>
